There is disquiet, anxiety and uncertainty within the Police service. Over 1000 police constables who graduated after 2016 claim they have never been paid according to their ranks as graduate police constables. Our investigations unit has been on this story for days, and it is turning out that no one, not even the police service commission is aware of these drastic changes effected in 2016 and which have led to a number of officers contemplating to resign. 